flowchart TD
    Input[Raw Text Input] --> Clean[Text Cleaning<br/>Remove HTML, URLs, Emails]
    Clean --> Lowercase[Lowercasing]
    Lowercase --> Punct[Punctuation Removal]
    Punct --> Tokenize[Tokenization<br/>Word Tokenization]
    Tokenize --> Stopwords[Stopword Removal]
    Stopwords --> Lemmatize[Lemmatization<br/>Optional]
    Lemmatize --> Filter[Filter Short Words<br/>Min Length 2]
    Filter --> Output[Processed Text Output]